Every challenge includes a virtual system. The main purpose is to discover any of the vulnerabilities of the system, using ethical hacking and penetration testing methods.
The main Operating System for reconnaisance or for executing the attacks is Kali Linux.

The main methods and commands used are included to the following summary git repository.
https://github.com/chreniuc/CTF

Other commands might be found on Google. Please focus on mastering the basic linux commands required for these challenges and also the usage of virtual box or other virtualization software.

